<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-01-21 13:39 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2713 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u l &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-HOME-PROJECT-BOS &LR;      01-21 1044
