<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-01-21 16:00 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2950 &Cx1f; taf-z
u e &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-ANTIQUES-COLUMN-NYT &LR;      01-21 1157
