<P>
   DDN-COX-SIRENS _ DAYTON, Ohio _ The days may be numbered for the
area's tornado warning siren system. Dayton, for one, says its
sirens are old and have a high rate of failure, and even
ineffective when they go off. Dayton is considering tanking it's
system and says some other communities, Huber Heights for one, have
already done so. (Bebbington, Dayton Daily News)
</P>
<P>
   PBP _ EVERGLADES (DEVELOPING) MIAMI, Fla. _ Combination of
