<P>
   TRIVIA-Q&AMP;A &QL;
</P>
<P>
   UNDATED _ On discerning the difference between apple juice and
apple cider. By ROGERS CADENHEAD. Story has moved in ``l''
lifestyle category. &QL; 
 &QL; 
 &QL;
</P>
<P>
   E N T E R T A I N M E N T &QL; 
 &QL; 
 &QL;
</P>
<P>
   TV-PROVIDENCE &QL;
</P>
<P>
   PASADENA, Calif. _ The critics hate the new NBC Friday-night
