<P>
   BERNARD SHAW SOCIETY, P.O. Box 1159, Madison Square Station, New
York, N.Y. 10159-1159. Next meeting, March 12, 8 p.m., at the
American Irish Historical Society, 991 Fifth Ave., at 80th Street.
