<P>
   MARK TWAIN CIRCLE OF NEW YORK. Contact: Peter Salwen, (212) 242
5546; e-mail: twaincircle(AT)salwen.com.
</P>
<P>
   W.B. YEATS SOCIETY OF NEW YORK, National Arts Club, 15 Gramercy
Park South, New York, N.Y. 10003.; (212) 780-0605. Web site:
www.panix.com/wlinden/yeats.shtml. The critic Helen Vendler will
