<HEADLINE>
OFFICIALS SEIZE NEARLY 5 TONS OF COCAINE IN RECORD BUST 

</HEADLINE>
  
 (For use by New York Times News Service clients)  (Eds.: Sub for minor editing) 
 
By CARLOS BYARS 
c.1998 Houston Chronicle 
 
<TEXT>
<P>
   HOUSTON _ Federal authorities seized a Panamanian-flag cargo
vessel with nearly five tons of cocaine in it in what officials
